room_title: Escape room "Abandoned Schoolroom" by Lubbock Panic Room in Lubbock
room_description: You and your team of secret agents have been tasked with the job of stealing a blueprint of a revolutionary design from Albert Winestein, a self-proclaimed boy genius. The blueprint is stashed somewhere in the classroom. You have 60 minutes before the class returns from a field trip, and only one chance to make history. Is your team up for the challenge?
